{
  "text": "Not all barriers to DER in the chemical industry can be characterised according to these four categories of lock-in. 1 Hence, we differentiate between 'normal' barriers and a special category of barriers which are (carbon) lock-ins. This distinction is relevant as carbon lock-in requires a different policy response [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
